name: edward, had you ever thought that the end of the world would come on 20.9.01?
name_en: Edward, Had You Ever Thought That the End of the World Would Come On 20.9.01?
lyrics:
Well it happened a few years ago
We're still pen friends at 17 years old
I waited for you everyday, did you know?
I scared to call you anyway, you didn't know

Then we met in a rainy day
I remember how you dressed that day
I forgot what I wanted to say when I saw your face
It's just like happened yesterday
But now you fall away
Oh now you fall away

Where are you now?
Why can't we be ourselves just like yesterday?
Edward, we were good pen friends
And did you ever believe me?
When I say "I don't need to be free
If you could only
Could only stay with me"
I don't need to be free
If you could stay with me
If you could stay with me

album.name: Zoo Is Sad, People Are Cruel
album.name_en: Zoo Is Sad, People Are Cruel
